{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our life in Gross Rosen was a-- was very much a mystery to us and how long-- what from here-- whether we will ever get out of this place.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But lo and behold, sometimes after three or four days-- and again, the days were-- night and day were running into one another, and nobody kept counting on-- on what day it is.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of those evenings, as we were sitting there in the laps of one another on the floor of the barrack, a SS guard came into the room with a list in his hand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he began to read names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, it-- you didn't have to be a scientist, even at that time, to recognize quickly that being on any kind of a list is better than remaining there in Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So myself, remembering from what I went through at that time, that night, I became extremely anxious as to whether they will have me on the list or not.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I knew that they were calling names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But who they are going to call and who they are not going to call, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my anxiety drove me nuts because I also began to think that my name-- my name being-- starting with a U would-- would take so long before they would get to me that maybe this is going to hurt me eventually that they are not going to get me on that list.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I went through hell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was sweating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was in fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it didn't even dawn on me at that time that they did not call in alphabetical order.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
